-> react-native--> mainly for app dev


npm- node package manager
npx- node package executer

To create react basic thing:
1}
// to create a utility/software
npx create-react-app 01basicreact // dont use this method as its time consuming and a bulky utility1

2} since npx is bulky we use *vite*
vite-->  https://vite.dev/


To create a new vite project use *npm create vite@latest*

u need to give:
1.project name
2.framework- react
3.variant- js
4.install npm - yes

then to run the js files in terminal: 
    check for the scripts within the package.json folder
    give npm run dev